# ── Sensitive files ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# WireGuard .conf files contain private keys — NEVER commit these.
*.conf

# ── Third-party binaries ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# wireguard.dll (wireguard-nt) is NOT distributed in this repository.
# Users must obtain it by installing WireGuard for Windows (wireguard.com/install/).
# Excluding all DLLs prevents accidental commits of unverified binaries.
*.dll

# ── Build artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Rust/Tauri
src-tauri/target/
src-tauri/gen/

# Frontend
node_modules/
dist/

# ── OS / Editor ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.user
.vscode/settings.json

# ── Claude Code session data ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/

# ── Debug logs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
